nas bikin.
 
Honestly, it's our first time coming to Tirmisha village, we
will enter this village together, we wanted to get to know
this village together like before.

18
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Û hurmet ji gundê Tirmîşa re û gundiyên Şikakora.
 
And respect to the village of Tirmisha and the villagers of
Shikakor.

19
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:08,000
Bi silav xwarina dayîka Efrînî, em ê derbasî gundê Tirmîşa
bin.
 
With the greetings of the Afrin mother, we will enter the
village of Tirmisha.

20
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:11,000
Em ê cem dayîkan rûnin, em ê pir çîrokan bi hevra zanibin.
 
We will sit with the mothers, we will know many stories
together.

21
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:17,000
Em ê silavê kefxweşiyan bidin xwediyê xwe, kesê ku vî gundî
da dimîne em ê sekne çûyîna wan bikin.
 
We will give joyful greetings to our hosts, the people
